TWEAK_QUICK_TOOLKIT_THUMBNAIL_ANIMATION					espen
	
	Sets the duration for a tumbnail animation

	A lower value will result in faster animation and fewer steps. Some configurations
	may have to reduce duration for proper performance

	Category			: performance
	Define				: THUMBNAIL_ANIMATION_DURATION
	Value				: 400
	Value for desktop	: 400
	Depends on			: nothing

